description:
Enjoy your favorite restaurants and stores, all in one place.
The Wolt app makes it easy to discover and order (almost) anything from your city. From delicious food and fresh groceries to pharmacy and pet supplies. Search by category, cuisine, restaurant or item! You can easily browse popular restaurants including McDonald's, KFC, Domino's, Pizza Hut, Papa Johns, Burger King and many more. Enjoy food delivery of burgers, pizza, sushi and other delicious items. If you prefer, you can pick up your order from the restaurant or store!

Order (almost) anything, on-demand.
Need to stock up on groceries? Can’t make it to the city? Wolt has you covered with groceries and essentials at your fingertips. Browse through the categories on Wolt and order anything, from pharmacy items to pet supplies. Anything you need, we’ve got you covered with our 40 000+ restaurants and stores. 

Top offers, only on Wolt.
Discover great offers on food, groceries and more! Browse hand-picked deals in the Wolt app and enjoy great savings. There’s offers on everything from food and groceries to electronics and homewares. Find the freshest deals in the app, including up to 50% off your order and €0 delivery fees!


Subscribe to Wolt+
If you’re looking for even bigger savings, Wolt+ is our popular subscription service offering €0 delivery fees, plus much more. As a Wolt+ member, you’ll unlock unbeatable deals and exclusive perks.

Make every occasion special with Wolt
We’ve made it easy to order and enjoy whatever you need. Get gifts for your loved ones, schedule orders for groceries and food, and save with deals on clothing and more! Wolt has you covered with everything to make moments special. Browse the selection of lovely flowers, chocolates, baked treats and more – delivered to your door in one hour or less.

Double Order
Need to order groceries and dinner? Now you can! Combine two local venues in one order with the same delivery fee. Place a Double Order and enjoy more convenience, for less!

Track every step
With every order, you can enjoy real-time tracking, and a minute-by-minute countdown. Whether you keep an eye on the tracker, or have other things to do, we'll keep you notified, so you know when your order is about to arrive.

Customer support
If something doesn’t go as planned, we’re ready to help – with customer support available 24/7. Our friendly team is there to help the 25+ countries we operate in and are ready to respond in seconds.

Payment
We think ordering Wolt should be as simple as possible. That’s why you can pay conveniently and securely with your credit card or Apple Pay. Whatever works for you.

Life simplified. Joy delivered. 
Wolt is currently available in 170+ cities located in Azerbaijan, Croatia, Cyprus, Czechia, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, Georgia, Germany, Greece, Hungary, Israel, Japan, Kazakhstan, Latvia, Lithuania, Malta, Norway, Poland,  Serbia,  Slovakia, Slovenia, Sweden. More are added all the time! Download Now and Unlock Essentials at your fingertips.

Wolt is an Editors’ Choice! 
Recognized by Apple as a top-rated app, Wolt delivers more than just food. Enjoy a seamless experience, from browsing our curated selection of restaurants to tracking your order in real-time.

Craving something delicious? Whether it's pizza, tacos, or your favourite fast food from Burger King and KFC, Bolt Food delivers straight to your door.

WHY CHOOSE BOLT FOOD?
- Real-time tracking: track your order and courier’s location from the restaurant to your doorstep.
- Convenient scheduling: plan ahead and order food or groceries in advance.
- Pickup options: prefer to grab your meal yourself? Use our pickup feature for easy collections.
- Takeaway deals and discounts: save on your favourite meals and snacks.
- Seamless payments: pay effortlessly using Google Pay, Apple Pay, or credit/debit cards.

HOW TO GET STARTED:
1. Set your delivery address.
2. Browse and pick meals, groceries, or snacks from your favourite local restaurants or stores.
3. Place your food order and pay securely.
4. Track your order in real-time.
5. Sit back and enjoy!

DISCOVER LOCAL AND GLOBAL FAVOURITES:
Explore a culinary world at your fingertips with Bolt Food. From beloved local restaurants to renowned fast food chains like McDonald's, get meals from your favourite restaurants delivered to your door.

*BOLT MARKET - QUICK GROCERY DELIVERY:
Need groceries or essentials delivered? Bolt Market brings everyday items like milk, bread, and coffee, as well as speciality products like pet supplies, cosmetics, or alcohol, right to your doorstep. Forget the long supermarket queues and shop smarter with Bolt Market.

*BOLT PLUS
With Bolt Plus, you can access exclusive benefits that save you time and money. For example, you can enjoy priority delivery for your orders, even during the busiest hours.

*GO OUT AND SAVE WITH DINEOUT
As convenient as it is to get food delivered to your door, some moments are worth making the trip out for. Find tables at nearby DineOut restaurants and get a discount off your meal. Just open the app, search for what you crave, and switch to the DineOut tab for in-restaurant offers. 

Bolt Food was created by the European super-app Bolt. It’s challenging the efficiency of the food and grocery delivery industry while helping restaurants and stores get more orders and enabling couriers to earn money.

Become a Bolt Food Courier partner:
Have a car, bike, or motorbike? Earn money delivering meals with Bolt Food: https://bolt.eu/en/food/courier/.

Partner with Bolt Food:
Are you a restaurant or grocery store? Boost your sales by joining Bolt Food: https://bolt.eu/en/food/partner/.

Get in touch with us via food@bolt.eu

Follow us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/boltfood.

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

Welcome to the new official McDonald’s app.

The app is filled with great offers specially tailored to you. Deals and discounts appear regularly so check back often to see what’s new.

The news section keeps you up to date with everything that’s going on in McDonald’s near you. Look here for new games and competitions.

The nutrition section provides information on our entire menu. We provide allergy advice and nutritional information on everything from the Big Mac to a single dip!

Use our restaurant finder to find your nearest McDonald’s. Filter your search based on opening hours, facilities and get directions from wherever you are.

Order your favorite KFC meals with just one touch! Experience seamless integration with delivery services and enjoy full compatibility with all major payment methods.

Track your order in real time—from kitchen to doorstep—with live updates and notifications every step of the way.

Get delicious KFC food delivered quickly and conveniently right to your home!

We’ve made ordering even easier! Download the new official Papa Johns pizza app and order your favorite pizza, sides, and drinks for delivery or takeaway. Want to dine in? No problem! Order online and eat at one of our pizza restaurants in Azerbaijan.


ABOUT PAPA JOHNS
Driven to be the best. Better Ingredients. Better Pizza.

The secret to success is much like the secret to making a better pizza − the more you put into it, the more you get out of it. We’re as hungry for perfection today as we were when we first opened our doors more than 30 years ago. And we’re driven to be the best at making innovative new products and recipes.

Quality is at our core. It’s the foundation we started with, from the first Papa Johns pizza that was made in a broom closet in Jeffersonville, IN, to now more than 5000 stores in 48 countries around the world.

Whether it’s our signature sauce, toppings, our original fresh dough, or even the box itself, we invest in our ingredients to ensure that we always give you the finest quality pizza.

For you, it’s not just a better pizza. It’s a family gathering, memorable birthday, work celebration or simply a great meal. It’s our goal to make sure you always have the best ingredients for every occasion.

Did Domino’s Azerbaijan just lunch their new app?
Oh Yes We Did!

	•	Enjoy quick ordering in just a few taps!
	•	Choose from Fast and Free Delivery or Takeaway.
	•	Save money and enjoy Great Foods with our Special Offers.
	•	Make your own pizza just the way you want it.
	•	Earn Points to get Free Pizza.
	•	Watch REAL-TIME the progress of your pizza while it’s being made until it gets to you on the Domino’s Tracker ® 
	•	Easily access to your favorite and recent orders for quick reordering

Food delivery service from grocery stores, cafes and restaurants

You can order both burgers and steaks, as well as products from grocery stores. Free delivery for your first order!

ALL NEARBY GROCERIES AND RESTAURANTS IN ONE APP
Get your groceries delivered from both popular stores and local markets. And for those who don't want to cook, you can find your favorite dishes from cafes and restaurants. In Yandex Eats, you can order a cooked pizza or ingredients for it.

ORDER FAST DELIVERY TO YOUR ADDRESS
Enter the delivery address — we will find the nearest store or restaurant to you and deliver the order as quickly as possible. On average food is delivered in 32 minutes after placing an order — even faster than you would get ready to go shopping.

TRACK YOUR ORDER 
In the app, you can find out the status of the order and the location of the courier.

USE FILTERS TO FIND EVERYTHING YOU NEED
With filters you can find a specific cuisine or dish with one click. “Burgers”, “Sushi”, “Pizza” — Yandex Eats has sets for every occasion.

DISCOUNTS AND SPECIAL OFFERS EVERY DAY 
In the app, you can place an order profitably: for example, get free delivery or a dish as a gift. In the section “Promotions” we collect the best offers from shops and restaurants every day.

Yandex Eats is an information service. Delivery zones, delivery times, and restaurant offers are limited. To learn more, go to eda.yandex. Fast delivery: the average order delivery time is 32 minutes according to data from January 18 to January 25, 2022.

developer: TYG TURKEY ELEKTRONIK TICARET HIZMETLERI VE YATIRIMLARI ANONIM SIRKETI
description:
Get one step closer to fast and easy ordering with hundreds of options, from your favorite restaurant and grocery chains to local businesses in your neighborhood.

• Dozens of Restaurants and Grocery Stores
With the Trendyol GO by Uber Eats app, you can easily order your favorite dishes from hundreds of restaurants like Burger King, McDonald's, Domino's Pizza, Little Caesars, Popeyes, Komagene, and Starbucks, as well as your groceries from local stores in your neighborhood. Your order will arrive at your door in minutes.

• Local Businesses
The products of dozens of local businesses in your neighborhood, such as water brands, butchers, greengrocers, pet shops, florists, and nut shops, are now at your fingertips. You no longer need to go to different places for your shopping.

• Hundreds of Delicious Options & Products
Find exactly what you want from hundreds of delicious options, exactly what you need from hundreds of grocery products, and many other products you need from Your Neighborhood Shops.

• Special Offers and Great Discounts Just for You
Thanks to campaigns and features like Eat More, Save More, Flash Sales, Buy More, Save More, and cart comparisons, you can enjoy discounts on both your food orders and grocery shopping.

• Live Tracking
With GO by Uber Eats courier deliveries, you can track your order live on the map and see where the courier is in real time. When the courier arrives on your street, you'll happily run to the door.

Fryday tətbiqi ilə tanış olun — dadlı burger dünyasında şəxsi bələdçiniz! Tətbiqimizi yükləyin və hər burgerin sevgi və bacarıqla yaradıldığı kulinariya şedevrlərinin heyrətamiz dünyasına dalın. Yalnız tətbiq istifadəçiləri üçün mövcud olan eksklüziv təkliflər və promosyonlar sizi gözləyir.

Fryday loyallıq sistemi hər sifarişinizi bayrama çevirəcək! Hər alış üçün xal toplayın və onları sevimli yeməklərinizlə dəyişdirin. Üstəlik, tətbiqdəki bildirişlər sayəsində Fryday şəbəkəsinin ən son xəbərləri və hadisələri ilə daima xəbərdar olun. Heç bir dadlı yeniliyi qaçırmayın!

Bizə qoşulun və bu gün hər sifarişdən zövq almağa başlayın. Cümə tətbiqi ilə sevdiyiniz burgerlər həmişə əlinizdə olacaq. Tətbiqi yükləyin və Cümə ilə birlikdə unikal tatlar və unudulmaz təcrübələr dünyasına səyahətə başlayın!

Get food delivery to your doorstep from thousands of amazing local and national restaurants. Find the meal you crave and order food from restaurants easily with the Uber Eats app. Track your order in real-time.

FIND YOUR FAVOURITE FOOD & RESTAURANTS
Order food from nearby restaurants and search by cuisine, restaurant name, dish, and meal. 
Food delivery options for you to order and enjoy such as pizza, burritos, burgers, sushi, fish and chips, doughnuts and Chinese takeout.
Prefer pickup? Skip the line and reservations and choose to pick up your order instead. Choose your favourite delivery options with the Uber Eats app now.

SUBSCRIBE TO UBER ONE
For £5.99 per month, Uber One subscribers enjoy £0 delivery fee and up to 5% off orders over £15 at participating non-grocery stores (and 5% off orders over £25 at participating grocery stores) available on Uber Eats. Members are also eligible for rewards, perks, coupons, and offers. View full Uber One Terms & Conditions in app.

ORDER ALMOST ANYTHING, ANYTIME
Order household needs from your favourite pharmacies, supermarkets, and pet shops. Baby food or nappies, pharmacy needs, beauty products and cosmetics. Grocery staples like bread and milk, bananas and produce, flowers and plants, packaged foods or frozen treats. 

You can even order alcoholic drinks including beer, wine, spirits and cocktails.*

SIMPLE DELIVERY ORDERING
Pick your food order from any menu and add it to your cart with a few taps. That’s it.
Uber Eats makes it easy to order food delivery online or through the app and have it delivered by restaurants and delivery people near you.
Or, schedule your order in advance for a delivery person to pick it up later. Your choice!

ORDER FOOD AHEAD WITH PICKUP
Now you can also order food ahead for Pickup instead of just ordering delivery. Select Pickup, add food items to your cart, and skip the lines to the restaurant to get your food.

REAL-TIME ORDER TRACKING
Track your food delivery order on a map as it heads your way.
See the estimated arrival time at your address.
Get notified when your order arrives.

FIND SOME OF YOUR FAVOURITE NATIONAL RESTAURANTS
Some of our food delivery partners include: Pizza Hut, Domino’s Pizza, Burger King, Dunkin', KFC, McDonald's, Starbucks, Subway, Taco Bell,Costa Coffee, Kaspas, Gourmet Burger Kitchen, Franco Manca, Dixy Chicken, Chipotle, Chaiiwala, Amigos Burgers Shakes, Papa John’s, Krispy Kreme.  

FIND PHARMACIES, GROCERY STORES, AND MORE
Order from grocery stores such as Asda, Sainsbury Supermarket, Waitrose, The Co-op, Iceland, M&S Food, and Londis. You can also order from pharmacies such as Boots via Uber Eats, as well as from other delivery partners in the convenience and retail spaces.

ABOUT UBER EATS
Uber Eats is the way to order the food you love through an easy delivery experience. Uber Eats is available in hundreds of cities around the world. Enter your delivery address to explore restaurant and grocery delivery options near you.

AVAILABLE INTERNATIONALLY

Join others in your city who use the Uber Eats app to order from their favourite restaurants and schedule delivery.

Uber Eats is currently available in cities and metro areas including Adelaide, Amsterdam, Atlanta, Auckland, Austin, Baltimore, Brussels, Cape Town, Chicago, Dallas, Denver, Johannesburg, Glasgow, London, Los Angeles, Madrid, Melbourne, Mexico City, Miami, Milan, Nashville, New Orleans, New York, Ottawa, Paris, Philadelphia, San Diego, San Francisco, Seattle, Stockholm, Sydney, Taipei, Tokyo, Toronto, Warsaw, and Washington DC. Uber Eats helps you find food delivery around the world. Order delivery in countries around the world. See full list of available countries on our website. Uber content/messages human- or machine-translated as per device settings; accuracy not guaranteed

*Alcohol is only available in select markets. Must be at least 18 to purchase. Item availability varies by market. See the Uber Eats app for details.

developer: Ata Express Elektronik Iletisim Tanitim Pazarlama Dagitim Sanayi Ve Ticaret Anonim Sirket
description:
Türkiye’nin indirim ve lezzeti buluşturan yemek sipariş uygulaması Tıkla Gelsin® ile tanış!
 
 
Online yemek siparişlerinde en sevdiğin lezzetlere kolayca ulaşmak, kampanyalar ve indirim avantajlarından faydalanmak istiyorsan adres belli. Tıkla Gelsin®, yemek yemek istediğin her an yanı başında. Kupon fırsatları ve Gel Al seçeneğiyle Tıkla Gelsin®, yemek siparişini hesaplı ve pratik hale getiriyor!
 
 
Neden Tıkla Gelsin®?
 
-Geniş restoran ağı: Türkiye'nin dört bir yanından binlerce restoran ve mutfak seçeneğine ulaş.
 
-Özel indirimler ve kampanyalar: Siparişlerinde indirimlerden faydalanma şansını yakala.
 
-Kolay ve hızlı sipariş: Kullanıcı dostu arayüz sayesinde siparişlerini birkaç dokunuşla tamamla.
 
-Canlı takip: Siparişinin tüm aşamalarını anlık takip et.
 
-Güvenli ödeme: Tıklapay Cüzdan, kredi kartı, banka kartı, yemek kartları ve diğer güvenli ödeme yöntemleri ile rahatça öde.
 
-Gel Al seçeneği: En sevdiğin lezzetleri sıra beklemeden ister restoranda ye ister paket olarak teslim al.
-Cüzdan özelliği: Tıklapay Cüzdan özelliği ile yaptığın yüklemelerde Tıkla Para kazan ve siparişlerinde kullan.
 
-Arkadaşını davet et: Arkadaşlarını Tıkla Gelsin® dünyasına davet ederek Tıkla Para’ları kap.
 
-Canlı destek: Chatbot 7/24 hizmetinde. Ayrıca 10:00-03:00 saatleri arasında canlı destek ekibimiz de yanında.
 
 
Yemek siparişi artık çok kolay
 
Online yemek dünyası ve sipariş uygulamalarının yıldızı Tıkla Gelsin®, her damak zevkine uygun restoran ve mutfak seçenekleriyle burada! Döner siparişi, pizza siparişi, tavuk yemekleri, içecekler ve diğer enfes lezzetler… Evde, işte ya da restoranda canın ne çekiyorsa birkaç tık uzağında. Tıkla Gelsin® kupon, kampanya ve indirim fırsatlarıyla enfes lezzetlere indirimlerle ulaşmanın tadını çıkar!
 
 
Gününü güzelleştirecek tüm yiyecek ve içecekler sen neredeysen orada
 
Sana Gelsin ile favori restoranını seç, istediğin yemekleri sepete ekle, online ya da kapıda dilediğin gibi öde. Siparişin hızlıca elinde!
 
 
Tıklapay ile kolayca öde
 
-Tıklapay Cüzdan’ına hızlı ve güvenli bir şekilde para yükle, siparişlerinde pratik ödeme deneyimini yaşa.
 
-Tıklapay Cüzdan ile sevdiklerine anında para transferi yap, işlemlerini birkaç tıkla tamamla.
 
 
Sepette indirim fırsatlarını kaçırma
 
Tıkla Gelsin® yemek sitesi ve yemek siparişi uygulaması, kullanıcılarına benzersiz kampanyalar ve indirimler sunuyor. Burger King® siparişi, Popeyes® siparişi, Arby’s® siparişi, Subway® siparişi, Sbarro® siparişi, Usta Dönerci®, Usta Pideci® siparişi, Amasya Et Ürünleri® siparişi, Milgo® siparişi… Tıkla Gelsin® ile hepsi aynı uygulamada! Yapman gereken tek şey sepetini enfes lezzetlerle doldurmak ve indirim fırsatlarını yakalamak! 
 
 
Tıkla Gelsin® ile siparişin kapında
 
Online yemek siparişi vermenin en güzel yanı da seçtiğin lezzetlere ev konforunda ve kolayca ulaşabilmek. Tıkla Gelsin® uygulamasıyla dilediğin lezzetler kapına geliyor. Böylece favori yiyecek ve içeceklerine evinden çıkmadan ulaşmanın keyfini çıkarabilirsin.
 
 
Tıkla Gelsin® lezzetleri her yerde: Restoranlarda Tıkla Gelsin®
 
Restoranlarda Tıklapay Cüzdan ve Tıkla Para ile ödeme yaparak özel avantajlardan yararlanmaya devam edebilirsin. Tıklapay Cüzdan özelliği, ilk yüklemeye özel yüklediğin miktara göre değişen oranda Tıkla Para kazandırıyor. Sonraki para yüklemelerinde kazancını çoğaltma şansın var! Üstelik Arkadaşını Davet Et özelliği de Tıkla Para kazanma fırsatı sunuyor.
 
Lezzetli yemeklerin keyfini çıkarmak hiç bu kadar kolay olmamıştı. Hemen Tıkla Gelsin®’i indir ve keyifli bir yemek deneyimi yaşa!
 
 
Daha Fazla Destek ve Bilgi için: bilgi@tiklagelsin.com
 
 
Youtube: www.youtube.com/@Tikla.Gelsin
 
 
X: x.com/tiklagelsin
 
 
Instagram: instagram.com/tikla.gelsin
 
 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/tiklagelsin1

Bishir is an innovative social platform created in Azerbaijan, designed for food lovers, chefs, and culinary enthusiasts to freely share their creativity, find inspiration, and connect with others. Starting from local culinary traditions, Bishir’s mission is to build a global community that shapes the future of the food industry.
Our goal is to create a vibrant space where anyone can easily share their kitchen knowledge and experiences, discover new and original recipes from around the world, and inspire one another through social interaction and support.
Bishir not only allows users to share their own recipes, but also offers the opportunity to earn income from their posts. Users can send digital gifts to the posts they love, and these gifts can be converted into real earnings for the content creators.
In the future, Bishir aims to become a leading platform that brings together the global culinary community by continuously adding new features to enrich the user experience and influence the worldwide food industry.
With Bishir, you’re not just sharing food — you’re becoming part of a global family of food lovers united by passion, creativity, and taste.

Sirab mobil tətbiqi Bakı, Sumqayıt, Abşeron və Naxçıvanda fəaliyyət göstərən onlayn su sifarişi xidmətidir. 
Siz tətbiq vasitəsilə bütün Sirab çeşidlərini bir kliklə olduğunuz yerə sifariş edə bilərsiniz.

70 il əvvəl bir tədqiqatçı tərəfindən kəşf edilən Sirab suyu Naxçıvan Muxtar Respublikasının Sirab kəndində yerləşir. Sirli suyun yatağından istifadə 1950-ci illərdən başlayıb və 1968-ci ildə Moskvanın Dövlət Ehtiyatlar Komissiyasında təsdiq edilmişdir. Sirab – torpağın bir neçə qat laylarından çıxır və tam təbii halı ilə yerində qablaşdırılır. İnsan orqanizmi üçün olduqca faydalı olan su 2003-cü ildə Sirab mineral sular zavodu Açıq Səhmdar Cəmiyyətinə çevrilmişdir. Hazırda Sirab Rusiya, Türkiyə, Ukrayna kimi nəhəng ölkələr də daxil olmaqla, 20-ə yaxın ölkəyə ixrac olunur. Hər damlasında həyat var!
